title: Ohio State at Minnesota | C.J. Stroud Looks Good in Opener vs Gophers | Sept. 2, 2021 | Highlights
author: Big Ten Network
description:
In his first start, C.J. Stroud threw for 294 yards and four touchdowns to help lead Ohio State to a 45-31 win over Minnesota.
